    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce a scheme to pay 15% of heating bill for some over 65s",
        "additional_details": "We think the Government paying 15% of some over 65\u2019s heating bill would leave money for them at the end of the month. However we do understand the rich pensioners do not need this as much so we think the Government should set a cut off point for who is and isn\u2019t getting heating paid for.",
        "background": "Research shows necessities such as heat and food are being chosen between for pensioners and we understand that through inflation some people don\u2019t have enough money per month.",
